| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4738 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff8158bd-bf55-59cc-9bcf-ed530db6eb4c"
